OL,3,CFormer deputy first minister says
OL,4,CHolyrood now needs 'significantly
OL,5,Cmore' MSPs
OL,7,FFormer Scottish deputy first minister
OL,8,FJim Wallace has said the number of
OL,9,FMSPs at Holyrood "needs to be looked
OL,10,Fat again".
OL,12,FThe former Scottish Liberal Democrat
OL,13,Fleader played a key role in
OL,14,Fdetermining the number of MSPs who
OL,15,Fwould sit in the Scottish Parliament
OL,16,Fwhen it was established back in 1999,
OL,17,Fbeing involved in negotiations with
OL,18,FLabour's George Robertson on the
OL,19,Fmatter.
