OL,3,CFormer deputy first minister says
OL,4,CHolyrood now needs 'significantly
OL,5,Cmore' MSPs
OL,7,FBut with Holyrood now having increased
OL,8,Fresponsibilities ` including powers
OL,9,Fover income tax in Scotland and social
OL,10,Fsecurity ` Lord Wallace, who was
OL,11,FScotland's first deputy first
OL,12,Fminister, now believes "significantly
OL,13,Fmore" MSPs are needed.
OL,15,FThe Liberal Democrat, who served as an
OL,16,FMP before joining the Scottish
OL,17,FParliament when it was established,
OL,18,Ftold how during his time at
OL,19,FWestminster he had been involved in
OL,20,Fdiscussions about how the new
OL,21,Fparliament would operate.
OL,26,@tD@XOUuD@EO]
