OL,3,CFormer deputy first minister says
OL,4,CHolyrood now needs 'significantly
OL,5,Cmore' MSPs
OL,7,FIt had already been agreed
OL,8,Fproportional representation would be
OL,9,Fused, with Lord Wallace recalling
OL,10,Fdiscussions from the time about how
OL,11,Fmany MSPs there should be.
OL,13,FSpeaking to the PA news agency, the
OL,14,FLiberal Democrat said: "George
OL,15,FRobertson and I had a haggle about
OL,16,Fwhat the numbers would be.
OL,18,FHe wanted 113, I wanted 145, and we
OL,19,Fgot 129. It was meeting in the middle.
OL,26,@vD@XOU
