OL,3,CFormer deputy first minister says
OL,4,CHolyrood now needs 'significantly
OL,5,Cmore' MSPs
OL,7,F"He got hell from the Labour Party for
OL,8,Fit. I got hell from the Liberal
OL,9,FDemocrats for it. So we both agreed we
OL,10,Fprobably got it right."
OL,12,FBut he added: "I think now the
OL,13,FParliament requires significantly
OL,14,Fmore, it has more responsibilities,
OL,15,Fnot least for tax and social security.
OL,17,F"I think 129 needs to be looked at
OL,18,Fagain."
