OL,3,CFormer deputy first minister says
OL,4,CHolyrood now needs 'significantly
OL,5,Cmore' MSPs
OL,7,FHe said Labour had acted
OL,8,F"unilaterally" to hold a referendum on
OL,9,Fwhether the devolved parliament should
OL,10,Fbe established ` with Liberal
OL,11,FDemocrats at the time opposed to such
OL,12,Fa ballot.
OL,14,FHowever Lord Wallace said: "In
OL,15,Fretrospect it was probably the right
OL,16,Fthing to do. Because I think it gave
OL,17,Fthe Parliament a political grounding
OL,18,Fwhich once done you can never roll
OL,19,Fback."
