OL,3,CFormer deputy first minister says
OL,4,CHolyrood now needs 'significantly
OL,5,Cmore' MSPs
OL,7,FIn the wake of the first Holyrood
OL,8,Felections, held on May 6 1999, Lord
OL,9,FWallace became Scotland's first deputy
OL,10,Ffirst minister, after the Scottish
OL,11,FLiberal Democrats went into coalition
OL,12,Fwith Labour ` who were the largest
OL,13,Fparty in the Scottish Parliament but
OL,14,Flacked an overall majority.
