OL,3,CFormer deputy first minister says
OL,4,CHolyrood now needs 'significantly
OL,5,Cmore' MSPs
OL,7,FHe said his party had "wargamed" for
OL,8,Fsuch an outcome during the first ever
OL,9,FHolyrood election campaign, and
OL,10,Fentered talks with then Scottish
OL,11,FLabour leader Donald Dewar ` who would
OL,12,Fbecome Scotland's first first minister
OL,13,F` with a costed programme based on key
OL,14,Fmanifesto commitments.
OL,16,FHowever he recalled the talks hitting
OL,17,Fa "stumbling block" over issues such
OL,18,Fas tuition fees, after his party made
OL,19,Fa pledge to scrap these during the
OL,20,F1999 elections.
OL,26,@oD@WOUoD@`O]yD@COUyD@SO]
