OL,3,CFormer deputy first minister says
OL,4,CHolyrood now needs 'significantly
OL,5,Cmore' MSPs
OL,7,FThe Labour-Liberal Democrat Scottish
OL,8,FExecutive went on to fulfil that
OL,9,Fpledge, introducing instead the
OL,10,FScottish graduate endowment scheme,
OL,11,Fwhich saw students charged a fee
OL,12,Finitially set at #2,000 only after
OL,13,Fcompleting their degree.
OL,15,FLord Wallace recalled: "Tuition fees
OL,16,Fwas always the big stumbling block. I
OL,17,Fthink on more than one occasion we
OL,18,Fthought that was it, we couldn't take
OL,19,Fit any further."
OL,26,@wD@XOU{D@PO]
