OL,3,CFormer deputy first minister says
OL,4,CHolyrood now needs 'significantly
OL,5,Cmore' MSPs
OL,7,FWhile he said the Liberal Democrats
OL,8,Fwould have been a "responsible
OL,9,Fopposition" the parties managed to
OL,10,Fresolve their differences and
OL,11,Festablished a coalition which would
OL,12,Fgovern in Scotland until 2007.
OL,14,FLord Wallace added he would have been
OL,15,F"disappointed" had he been unable to
OL,16,Fstrike a deal with Labour, but added:
OL,17,F"We got the breakthrough, and that
OL,18,Fallowed us to support Donald to become
OL,19,Ffirst minister."
