OL,7,FHowever he contrasted the treatment he
OL,8,Fgot then with that handed out to the
OL,9,FScottish Greens when Humza Yousaf
OL,10,Fended the powersharing deal between
OL,11,Ftheir party and the SNP.
OL,13,FSaying Mr Dewar had called "to say
OL,14,Fcould we have a chat", he said he told
OL,15,Fto come in via the back door at Bute
OL,16,FHouse in Edinburgh ` the official
OL,17,Fresidence of the Scottish first
OL,18,Fminister ` to avoid being seen.
